            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", but what Rolls-Royce is showing off looks quite compelling.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "alt": "Rolls-Royce Reveals Dawn Silver Bullet Collection ",
        "src": "__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2020/03/P90386043_highRes_rolls-royce-dawn-sil.jpg"
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "According to the company, the overall message of the Dawn Silver Bullet is one of frivolity and decadence. It’s supposed to be a callback to the glamorous days of Hollywood before the Great Depression and the opulent cars driven by the most famous stars.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "It’s no coincidence that this model is being called the Silver Bullet, besides a hat tip to the new ultra-metallic silver Bespoke paint. After all, silver has been used throughout Rolls-Royce history, including for the ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "Silver Wraith",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "https://buy.motorious.com/vehicles/search/Rolls-Royce/Silver%20Wraith",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", Silver Spectre, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "Silver Shadow",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "https://buy.motorious.com/vehicles/search/Rolls-Royce/Silver%20Shadow",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", Silver Dawn, ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
                "text": "Silver Cloud",
                "type": "text",
                "version": 1
              }
            ],
            "direction": "ltr",
            "format": "",
            "indent": 0,
            "type": "link",
            "rel": null,
            "target": null,
            "title": null,
            "url": "https://buy.motorious.com/vehicles/search/Rolls-Royce/Silver%20Cloud%20III",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": ", Silver Silence, and Silver King.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Bold, carefree non-conformity is supposed to be communicated with the flowing lines. If the renderings are any indication, this version of the Rolls-Royce Dawn will feature more swooping exterior lines, like its car designs of a century ago. It’s not like anyone drives a Rolls to blend in, but this model has the potential to really stand out, even among other high-end cars.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2020/03/P90386042_highRes_rolls-royce-dawn-sil.jpg",
        "alt": "Rolls-Royce Reveals Dawn Silver Bullet Collection "
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "We can see several interesting details in the released renderings. Contrasting with the silver paint are dark highlights, including around the headlights and front bumper finisher. Rolls-Royce will use part-polished wheels with a unique translucent shadow finish plus a silver pinstripe, which no doubt will be mesmerizing whether the car is sitting or rolling down the road. There’s also a vapor-blasted titanium finish for the Aero Cowling windbreak show in great detail. The Silver Bullet name will be in a contrast machined text, so it stands out in a big way.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "At a time when some automakers are getting away from tactile elements for car interiors, it’s refreshing to hear Rolls-Royce is putting that quality front-and-center for the Dawn Silver Bullet. For example, there is carbon fiber but it’s an open-pore variety, so you get a dash of new material with some texture to it. Quilted leather with contrast stitching is also confirmed, while real wood could possibly be available, although the open-pore carbon fiber might displace it.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "__GHOST_URL__/content/images/2020/03/P90386045_highRes_rolls-royce-dawn-sil.jpg",
        "alt": "Rolls-Royce Reveals Dawn Silver Bullet Collection "
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "You can rest assured the Rolls-Royce Dawn Silver Bullet Collection cars will be highly coveted by collectors in the coming years. The automaker is looking to drum up more interest in them through a variety of marketing efforts, including holding Silver Bullet Drives or exclusive road trips for owners.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
        "direction": "ltr",
        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "paragraph",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "More Luxurious Rides",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
        ],
